{"id":23215,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Beautiful_Mind_(movie)","text":"\"A Beautiful Mind\" is a 2001 biographical movie about the mathematician John Nash and his experiences of schizophrenia. It is set in Massachusetts and New Jersey. It stars Russell Crowe, Ed Harris, Jennifer Connelly, Christopher Plummer, and Paul Bettany. It was directed by Ron Howard.\nThe movie is based on a book by Sylvia Nasar.\nThe movie won four Academy Awards, including the Academy Award for Best Picture. Connelly won for Best Supporting Actress.","categories":[],"infobox_types":["film"],"annotations":[{"uri":"Mathematician","surface_form":"mathematician","offset":58},{"uri":"John_Forbes_Nash","surface_form":"John Nash","offset":72},{"uri":"Schizophrenia","surface_form":"schizophrenia","offset":105},{"uri":"Massachusetts","surface_form":"Massachusetts","offset":133},{"uri":"New_Jersey","surface_form":"New Jersey","offset":151},{"uri":"Russell_Crowe","surface_form":"Russell Crowe","offset":172},{"uri":"Ed_Harris","surface_form":"Ed Harris","offset":187},{"uri":"Jennifer_Connelly","surface_form":"Jennifer Connelly","offset":198},{"uri":"Christopher_Plummer","surface_form":"Christopher Plummer","offset":217},{"uri":"Paul_Bettany","surface_form":"Paul Bettany","offset":242},{"uri":"Ron_Howard","surface_form":"Ron Howard","offset":275},{"uri":"Sylvia_Nasar","surface_form":"Sylvia Nasar","offset":319},{"uri":"Academy_Award","surface_form":"Academy Award","offset":352},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture","surface_form":"Academy Award for Best Picture","offset":382},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Supporting_Actress","surface_form":"Best Supporting Actress","offset":431}]}